{
  "id": "adv_event_2405_01_05_02",
  "title": "その覚悟は\n出来てる？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "こんなはずじゃなかったのに……\nどうして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This wasn’t how it was supposed to be…\nWhy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 4.6126280784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.8747227322
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。愛とこころには、先に帰ってもらったよ\n……酷いステージだったね、莉央",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work. I let Ai and Kokoro head back first.\n…That was a terrible stage‚ Rio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8747227322,
      "endTime": 13.583135665499999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.6517909282
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "……そうね。BIG4を目指すなんて言っておきながら\nなんてザマよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You’re right. We say we’re aiming for BIG4‚\nbut look at us…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.7747227322,
      "endTime": 19.9227995525,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.1361330002
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "新人相手に、あんなギリギリの勝利だなんて\n正直、負けてもおかしくはなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To barely win against rookies…\nhonestly‚ it wouldn’t have been strange if we had lost.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.1361330002,
      "endTime": 27.1519604652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.3452938368
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "……理由は、よく分かっているつもりよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I think I know the reason.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.3452938368,
      "endTime": 30.6405092528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.8538426052
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。僕と莉央の連携が、出来ていなかった\nそれが大きく減点された原因だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. You and I weren’t in sync.\nThat was the main reason our score was so low.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.8538426052,
      "endTime": 38.055293716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.3205235134
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、莉央。今回のことで思ったんだけど……\n僕達は、トップアイドルを目指してるんだった……よね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Rio. I’ve been thinking about this…\nWe’re aiming to become top idols… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.3205235134,
      "endTime": 47.778120101599995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.9871901801
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、そうよ\nそれが私達がアイドルを続けている理由でしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ that’s right.\nThat’s the reason we’re continuing to be idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.9871901801,
      "endTime": 53.062904577400005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.2762378345
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "そのためなら、何を捨ててもいい\n――その覚悟は出来てる？　例えば、僕達らしさとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that’s the case‚ we can throw anything away.\n…Are you prepared to do that? For example‚ our identity.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.2762378345,
      "endTime": 62.4851495395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.6762378345
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "それは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.6762378345,
      "endTime": 64.396695436,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.5966954479
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "僕は正直、分からないし、迷ってるんだ\nその迷いが、パフォーマンスに出てしまった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To be honest‚ I don’t know‚ and I’m conflicted.\nThat conflict showed in our performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.5966954479,
      "endTime": 73.5402558574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.7300287812
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "莉央。君は――僕達は、誰のために\nなんのために、トップアイドルを目指すの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio. You—no‚ we—who are we doing this for?\nAnd why are we aiming to become top idols?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.7300287812,
      "endTime": 83.8942465394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.0966954479
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめんなさい、葵。今はまだ、分からないわ\nでもその答えを出さない限り――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’m sorry‚ Aoi. Right now‚ I don’t know.\nBut unless we find that answer――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.0966954479,
      "endTime": 92.8051083812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.9917752196
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "私達はこれ以上前に進むことが出来ない\nそんな気がする……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel like we won’t be able to move forward anymore.\n…That's how I feel…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.9917752196,
      "endTime": 98.2461600234,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}